title: Cannes Cast And Crew Of Holy Spider By Ali Abbasi On The Red Carpet AFP

sources.title: Cannes Cast And Crew Of Holy Spider By Ali Abbasi On The Red Carpet Afp
sources.description: Cannes Cast And Crew Of Holy Spider By Ali Abbasi On The Red Carpet AFP 22. maj 2022 The cast and crew of "Holy Spider" by Iranian-Danish director Ali Abbasi, in the running for the Palme d'or, walk the red carpet for the premiere at the Cannes film festival.
